# ============================
# Project Specific
# ============================

## Ignore generated images only
*.generated.png
*.generated.jpg
*.generated.jpeg
*.generated.gif

## Docs (if they're autogenerated)
docs/
*.docx
*.doc
*.pdf

## Exclude all .txt except specific ones
*.txt
!README.txt
!README.md
!LICENSE.txt
!LICENSE.md

# ============================
# Keep important files
# ============================

## Keep .gitignore and .gitattributes
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes

## Keep documentation
!*.md
!*.txt
!LICENSE*
!README*

## Keep project files
!*.csproj
!*.sln

## Keep all source code
!*.cs

## Keep Config folder structure (but not sensitive files)
!Config/
Config/*.json
!Config/appsettings.template.json
!Config/*.cs

## Keep Models, Commands, Services, etc.
!Models/
!Commands/
!Services/
!Repositories/
!Events/
!Data/
!Models/**/*.cs
!Commands/**/*.cs
!Services/**/*.cs
!Repositories/**/*.cs
!Events/**/*.cs
!Data/**/*.cs

